{"title":"初来乍到HEXO","date":"2019-04-22T11:50:56.000Z","link":"post/闪亮登场","updated":"2019-05-03T11:38:26.000Z","content":"<p>Welcome to <a href=\"https://hexo.io/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Hexo</a>! This is your very first post. Check <a href=\"https://hexo.io/docs/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">documentation</a> for more info. If you get any problems when using Hexo, you can find the answer in <a href=\"https://hexo.io/docs/troubleshooting.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">troubleshooting</a> or you can ask me on <a href=\"https://github.com/hexojs/hexo/issues\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">GitHub</a>.</p>\n<h2 id=\"Quick-Start\">Quick Start<a href=\"post/闪亮登场#Quick-Start\"></a></h2><h3 id=\"NO-1-全局安装hexo\">NO.1 全局安装hexo<a href=\"post/闪亮登场#NO-1-全局安装hexo\"></a></h3><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">$ npm install -g hexo-cli</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>More info: <a href=\"https://hexo.io/zh-cn/docs/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Writing</a></p>\n<h3 id=\"NO-2-创建仓库\">NO.2  创建仓库<a href=\"post/闪亮登场#NO-2-创建仓库\"></a></h3><ol>\n<li>在库中创建一个  userename + github.io 的👖</li>\n<li>创建 👖 的时候取消掉自带的md文件选项文件</li>\n<li>接下来打开终端开始骚操作</li>\n</ol>\n<h3 id=\"NO-3-生成blog目录-👀\">NO.3 生成blog目录 👀<a href=\"post/闪亮登场#NO-3-生成blog目录-👀\"></a></h3><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">$ hexo init &lt;folder&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">$ <span class=\"built_in\">cd</span> &lt;folder&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">$ npm install</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h3 id=\"NO-4-挂载到GitHub上-🥁\">NO.4 挂载到GitHub上 🥁<a href=\"post/闪亮登场#NO-4-挂载到GitHub上-🥁\"></a></h3><p>在myblog根目录找到<code>_config.yml</code>中的下面这段修改成自己的GitHub路径</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">deploy:</span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"built_in\">type</span>: git</span><br><span class=\"line\">  repo: https://github.com/ragnar-document/ragnar-document.github.io.git</span><br><span class=\"line\">  branch: master</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h3 id=\"NO-5-开车踩油门-🚗\">NO.5     开车踩油门    🚗<a href=\"post/闪亮登场#NO-5-开车踩油门-🚗\"></a></h3><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">$ hexo clean 清理缓存</span><br><span class=\"line\">$ hexo g 打包项目</span><br><span class=\"line\">$ hexo d 一键部署</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>大概到这就已经新手上路啦 😂发一个喜极而泣的表情🎉一下</p>\n<h3 id=\"NO-6-写一下自己不会看给别人看的东西-🤦‍♀️\">NO.6  写一下自己不会看给别人看的东西 🤦‍♀️<a href=\"post/闪亮登场#NO-6-写一下自己不会看给别人看的东西-🤦‍♀️\"></a></h3><p>生成 🆕 文件</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">$ hexo new [layout] &lt;title&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>more info <a href=\"https://hexo.io/zh-cn/docs/writing\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">传送门</a></p>\n<h3 id=\"NO-7-themes-主题设置\">NO.7 themes 主题设置<a href=\"post/闪亮登场#NO-7-themes-主题设置\"></a></h3><p>主题传送门在此 <a href=\"https://hexo.io/themes/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">点  &gt;&gt;&gt; 🐶    狗头</a></p>\n<p>在根目录的_config 🀄️ 找到<code>theme: xxxx</code> 把你下载的主题文件名替换掉 <code>xxx</code> </p>\n<p>重复    NO.5    第二步和第三步</p>\n<h3 id=\"NO-8-为什么选择HEXO呢？\">NO.8     为什么选择HEXO呢？<a href=\"post/闪亮登场#NO-8-为什么选择HEXO呢？\"></a></h3><p>因为他他他他好欺负哈哈哈😂</p>\n","prev":{"title":"关于滚动吸顶的方法","link":"post/滚动吸顶的方法"},"plink":"http://yoursite.com/post/闪亮登场/","toc":[{"title":"Quick Start","id":"Quick-Start","index":"1","children":[{"title":"NO.1 全局安装hexo","id":"NO-1-全局安装hexo","index":"1.1"},{"title":"NO.2  创建仓库","id":"NO-2-创建仓库","index":"1.2"},{"title":"NO.3 生成blog目录 👀","id":"NO-3-生成blog目录-👀","index":"1.3"},{"title":"NO.4 挂载到GitHub上 🥁","id":"NO-4-挂载到GitHub上-🥁","index":"1.4"},{"title":"NO.5     开车踩油门    🚗","id":"NO-5-开车踩油门-🚗","index":"1.5"},{"title":"NO.6  写一下自己不会看给别人看的东西 🤦‍♀️","id":"NO-6-写一下自己不会看给别人看的东西-🤦‍♀️","index":"1.6"},{"title":"NO.7 themes 主题设置","id":"NO-7-themes-主题设置","index":"1.7"},{"title":"NO.8     为什么选择HEXO呢？","id":"NO-8-为什么选择HEXO呢？","index":"1.8"}]}]}